      <title>耶伦在被问及日元问题时表示货币干预应该很少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/yellen-asked-on-yen-says-currency-interventions-should-be-rare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当被问及对日本为解决日元兑美元汇率下滑问题而可能采取的任何行动有何反应时，美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，对外汇市场的干预应该很少见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/yellen-asked-on-yen-says-currency-interventions-should-be-rare</guid>
